New in version 1.0.2, 16 November 2014:
    * bug fix in fragment generation (last 2 based of transcript were never sequenced)

New in version 1.0.1, 5 November 2014:
    * corrected size parameter specification in simulate_experiment. (If size was provided as vector, subsets taken were too short, and error was thrown).

Version 0.99.2 became part of bioc-release and was released as Version 1.0.0.

New in version 0.99.2, 22 September 2014:
    * fixed bug where read names were incorrect in output fasta files
    * updated vignette
    * added biocViews
    * fixed coding style

Package submission, version 0.99.0, 18 July 2014